     _Section_: Time Dependent::Propagation
     _Type_: integer
     _Default_: 1500
     Number of time steps in which the total integration time is
     divided;  in previous notation, _N_.

   * *TDTimeStep*
     _Section_: Time Dependent::Propagation
     _Type_: float
     _Default_: 0.07 a.u.
     Time-step for the propagation;  in previous notation, \delta t.



